hopobject.body: Whereabouts are you from? dr numb zalf kopen Later, with two on and no outs, three Twins errors helped the Indians tack on two runs in the sixth inning to push their advantage to 4-0. Asdrubal Cabrera laid down a textbook sacrifice bunt to move the runners over into scoring position, but a throwing error on pitcher Scott Diamond allowed Carlos Santana to score from third. Two batters later, Yan Gomes hit a sacrifice fly to left field to score Ryan Raburn.
